title: Deep Heat
overview: Quick-witted, rebellious Holly, a frustrated wannabe wrestler faces the challenge of a lifetime. When all of Boss Pro's top wrestlers are poached by her brother Nick Nitro, Holly's mum, Pam is left devastated as it looks as though it's game over for the North West's oldest pro-wrestling company. But, if Holly can bring together Boss Pro's remaining gang of misfits, the company might just surviveâ€¦if only Pam would allow Holly to wrestle herself.
